reviews.text: Such satisfying meal at French Table! A nice place for relaxing and tasting finely.

Dinner with my teams tonight ! thank you chef Michael for the delicious foods . Highly recommend Pan-fried Foie Gras and French Foie Gras Ravioli with Black Truffle cream . Rest of the menu are also excellent.  Quality food with reasonable price. Definitely will come again with my own bottle coz no corkage fee.

reviews.text: 服務態度好好，食物有水準, 由其是鴨，食過咁多間最好食呢間

Lunch 啲價錢都好貴，在樓上舖而言。 不是太多人lunch time但服務好慢。
最欣賞是嗰杯咖啡但都要加錢cappuccino。
其他略嫌鹹了一點但這個都是個人口味而言。
過咗開心嘅一個晚上, 氣氛好好, 食物新鮮
好有heart既小店！特別係個鵝肝醬 本人從來不吃的 自上次食過呢度chef自家製的鵝肝醬 令我一試難忘 推介👍🏼👍🏼
Such satisfying meal at French Table! A nice place for relaxing and tasting finely.
